

## TESTING

    npm test


## DEVELOPMENT

    coffee migrate.coffee
    npm run-script dev-server


## DEPLOY

    cd deployment/

    # Install roles
    ansible-galaxy install -r requirements -p roles

    ansible-playbook playbook.yml -i production.txt --extra-vars "dude_env=production"

    shipit production deploy-dude
    shipit production start-app


## DEPLOY ON VAGRANT

    # create deployment/vagrant.txt with VM IP
    # could be anything, I'm using 192.168.33.80

    ansible-playbook playbook.yml -i vagrant.txt -u vagrant --private-key=~/.vagrant.d/insecure_private_key --extra-vars "dude_env=production"
